{"tid":2509292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《英雄本色》曾激勵韓國人民，助我們度過軍事獨裁政權的高壓時代","createTime":"2021-04-29T10:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T11:05:51.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29d62583dae59ed8910a2eea03601da1f9b10b2c","tid":2509292,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:21:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jozev1969/posts/10158180648276009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjozev1969%2Fposts%2F10158180648276009&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=ac96c02c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jozev1969/posts/10158180648276009</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf9o34SdeU1m39xuJ6XwXZGLnaLeMNnxpZZ53VHkWygSv?filename=4aTgXgi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4aTgXgi.jpg&h=2f560f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：喬靖夫<br />\n<br />\n在《奔向未來日子》(英雄本色II主題曲)一個韓國樂團演奏版的YouTube底下，有位網友特意以英文向香港人留言。<br />\n<br />\nhttps://youtu. be/mJfgb7ySgeo<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，當年我們拍的《英雄本色》電影，曾經對韓國人民有很大的激勵作用，幫助他們度過軍事獨裁政權的高壓時代，因此韓國人至今一直對《英雄本色》具有深厚的感情。<br />\n<br />\n最後他亦勉勵香港人，最終必能像韓國人一樣，成功改變命運。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mJfgb7ySgeo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmJfgb7ySgeo&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=194a6e83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mJfgb7ySgeo</a><br />\n<br />\n喬靖夫:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ujVjfMMpSOs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FujVjfMMpSOs&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=b4a97501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ujVjfMMpSOs</a>"},{"pid":"4dc214a22f4f6ba15759f2e1815f879f00e96d8f","tid":2509292,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"廿年前做野有個韓仔 dancer 都有講英雄本色呢套戲係係好多韓國人既 favorite ，但佢冇講固中原因。"},{"pid":"aef1df0655626a74ef277081df9b2ecd3a1d480f","tid":2509292,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"RM香港篇都有唱當年情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}